{"tid":103319,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"被拖欠薪金 冇錢交學費點算好","createTime":"2017-02-01T09:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T01:52:26.000Z","uid":21391,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afb21cde44ccb22a77d5d4eeb627ee2b21b90160","tid":103319,"uid":21391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"小弟窮學生一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直返part time 賺生活費同學費錢<br />\n我一直都係炒散 因為時間彈性啲 <br />\n我12月開始長返一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為之前都返過幾日 加上佢又有同我簽約打卡 應該幾穩陣諗住可以長做<br />\n但係我12月到而家都冇出過糧<br />\n我12月尾已經打去催佢出糧比我<br />\n每星期都有打去問 佢都同我講下星期下星期 一路拖<br />\n一星期又一星期 到而家一蚊都未到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1月我keep住有返 再前一個幾星期office同我講過年前會全數出哂12月同1月既糧...<br />\n點知過年都未出 而家都未出 <br />\n我前日再催佢話星期3會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家都未出比我<br />\n我就黎要交學費啦 好無助 我可以點做<br />\n而家窮到搵個錢刮沙都冇啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b96fdd84f8da7f331b232ab173efd4fd887d393","tid":103319,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"google la"},{"pid":"bfd253f3ec037433e30385cbc00dc61b5b3ab8c4","tid":103319,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"開名"},{"pid":"a5e3beb20964cbc8782ab17bf1abca9eec2f4bf2","tid":103319,"uid":21391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>google la</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果去勞工處告佢既有排都拎唔到舊錢 我趕住交學費 冇得拖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dcef426e981da83c74d56ce1e29e613858a43d","tid":103319,"uid":24779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"試過Send勞工處拖欠薪金熱線條個電話比佢，本身不斷藍剔我，電話又唔聽，一send即刻死狗咁話聽日入票，之後好快就收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a120f5a3cb6d9c1d2668e88ff9d8e90378127bb6","tid":103319,"uid":21391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過Send勞工處拖欠薪金熱線條個電話比佢，本身不斷藍剔我，電話又唔聽，一send即刻死狗咁話聽日入票，之後好快就收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前都有試過第二間返過幾日 大慨有一千頭左右冇出比我 條友藍剔我好多次 但果個冇簽約既 我諗追唔到所以就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解次次都拖欠我薪金"},{"pid":"87b5e1e3237e25a00c00e2ddfff75234bd58482e","tid":103319,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76cf6cf590565c267764144c0bbf34eea25afa32","tid":103319,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:20:41.000Z","msg":"申請defer交學費囉"},{"pid":"92c08441f29fb57467fdee156462fa44412a4f7d","tid":103319,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:22:39.000Z","msg":"巴打邊間U?如果係CU既話唔洗怕啦，就算你今年年尾先交返學費既話都係罰多兩舊水咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40df86e65f9ae42d510e3255a63c81459475ae1e","tid":103319,"uid":21391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差幾多學費?</blockquote><br />\n1萬鬆啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢出埋就夠 兩個月糧夠錢交"},{"pid":"95470081c94da890c4caf7c6fc0ae055b5f3e08a","tid":103319,"uid":21391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打邊間U?如果係CU既話唔洗怕啦，就算你今年年尾先交返學費既話都係罰多兩舊水咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係BU"},{"pid":"fe8a60c4df87b9c8c7dbbe389c5720bcddad5c88","tid":103319,"uid":21391,"